import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import { useParams } from 'react-router-dom'; import axios from 'axios'; import './Coin.css'; const Coin = () => { const params = useParams(); const [coin, setCoin] = useState({}); const url = `https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/coins/${params.coinId}`; useEffect(() => { axios.get(url) .then((res) => { setCoin(res.data); }) .catch((error) => { console.log(error); }); }, []); return (

{coin.name}

Rank # {coin.market_cap_rank}
{coin.image ? : null}

{coin.name}

{coin.symbol}

{coin.market_data ?

{coin.market_data.current_price}

: null}
1h 24h 7d 14d 30d 1yr
{coin.market_data?.price_change_percentage_24h_in_currency ? coin.market_data.price_change_percentage_1h_in_currency.eur: null} {coin.market_data.price_change_percentage_24h_in_currency.eur} {coin.market_data.price_change_percentage_7d_in_currency.eur} {coin.market_data.price_change_percentage_14d_in_currency.eur} {coin.market_data.price_change_percentage_30d_in_currency.eur} {coin.market_data.price_change_percentage_1yr_in_currency.eur}

24 hour Low

{coin.market_data.low_24h.eur}

24 hour High

{coin.market_data.high_24h.eur}

Market Cap

{coin.market_data.market_cap.eur}

Circulating supply

{coin.market_data.circulating_supply}

About

{coin.description.fr}

); }; export default Coin;
